text: Reimu Hakurei: This music is getting on my nerves
Benben Tsukumo: You don't like it?
Yatsuhashi Tsukumo: May we play something else?
Reimu Hakurei: No, no and no! You're giving me headache...
Yatsuhashi Tsukumo: Then drink a bit
Benben Tsukumo: You'll feel better then
Yatsuhashi Tsukumo: And enjoy our music!
Reimu Hakurei: Tch, even if you play some good combos,
Reimu Hakurei: I will show you that silence is golden!
